{"tid":2512030,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"全港5.2萬私樓空置 大埔成重災區 平均每9個屋有一間丟空","createTime":"2021-05-01T11:03:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T13:42:29.000Z","uid":283477,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"fa6fb0a52c8ac73ded7fc679cd5ba35ab7cbda0b","tid":2512030,"uid":283477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T11:03:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2945963\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2945963&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNt5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=4bf0e9f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2945963</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去年私樓落成量大增，遇上疫情爆發，挾高私人住宅空置稅。據差估署《香港物業報告2021》數據指出，去年整體私樓空置率為4.3%，按年增加0.6個百分點，大埔區成為重災區，多達4,372伙空置，空置率11%，平均每9個單位就有一間空置。<br />\n<br />\n據報告指出，去年全港空置單位共52366伙，較2019年的44892伙，增加17%或7474伙，佔全港私樓總存量達4.3%，按年上升0.6個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以單位類型計算，空置最嚴重仍然是豪宅類別，空置率達10%，但較2019年回落3.8個百分點，空置的豪宅單位亦減少27%或1045伙。<br />\n<br />\n至於地區作劃分，重災區則為大埔區、屯門區及西貢區(包括將軍澳)，當中大埔區空置率達11.2%，按年再升1.8個百分點，涉及4372伙，相信與兩年區內白石角有大量新盤入伙有關。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咩大埔真係甘多空置？<br />\n但又唔見大埔樓跌。。<br />\n甚至同市區其他區差唔多價<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n乜"},{"pid":"0468778eed8150aaabc3c91b4dc6513126f4217c","tid":2512030,"uid":4826,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T11:04:22.000Z","msg":"收空置稅未，越高越好，屌佢老母移民丫嗱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73ba694bfdcf94d18509bc644e933c0300597b95","tid":2512030,"uid":159876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa6fb0a52c8ac73ded7fc679cd5ba35ab7cbda0b","tid":2512030,"uid":283477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T11:03:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2945963\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2945963&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlg